  "faq": {
    "title": "Frequently Asked Questions",
    "q1": "What happens after the 14-day trial ends?",
    "a1": "After the trial, you'll be switched to your chosen plan. If you cancel, your data is kept for 30 days.",
    "q2": "Does the system work without internet?",
    "a2": "Core features (adding customers, creating orders) work offline. Data syncs when the connection is restored.",
    "q3": "Is my data secure?",
    "a3": "Yes, all data is protected with SSL encryption. Daily backups are taken automatically.",
    "q4": "Can I use it across multiple branches?",
    "a4": "The Enterprise plan supports multiple branches and data sharing between them.",
    "q5": "How long does setup take?",
    "a5": "No installation needed — it runs in the browser. You can start within 5 minutes of signing up.",
    "q6": "Do you support VAT invoicing for UAE and Saudi Arabia?",
    "a6": "Yes — UAE 5% and KSA 15% VAT are built in. Each invoice includes your VAT registration number and a full tax breakdown.",
